<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="page-container">
  <div class="page-header" data-animate="slide-up">
    <h1>Shipping Information</h1>
    <p>Everything you need to know about getting your items delivered safely and on time.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose" data-animate="fade-in">
    <h2>Standard Shipping</h2>
    <p>We offer flat-rate standard shipping on all orders under $50. Orders over $50 qualify for free standard shipping. Standard shipping typically takes 3-5 business days depending on your location.</p>

    <h2>Expedited Shipping</h2>
    <p>Need it faster? We offer 2-Day and Next-Day shipping options at checkout. Orders must be placed by 2:00 PM EST to be processed the same day. Expedited shipping rates are calculated dynamically based on package weight and destination.</p>

    <h2>International Shipping</h2>
    <p>ShopZone ships worldwide! International delivery times vary widely depending on customs processing in your country. Please note that customers are responsible for any import duties, taxes, or brokerage fees.</p>

    <h2>Order Tracking</h2>
    <p>Once your order has shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number. You can also view your tracking information by logging into your ShopZone account and visiting the "My Orders" section.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
